      "title": "Kanchana - Nasir leaves for Qatar",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera and Minister of Environment Nasir Ahmed are scheduled to leave for Qatar this afternoon (27) to discuss fuel and labor.",
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said that priority will be given to obtain fuel from the Government of Qatar."
      ],
